name: PregnancyMeditations
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pregnancy meditations
des: Pregnancy Meditations provides multiple mindfulness practices to help with anything an expecting mother could need. It is recommended to set aside some time every day for some meditation to alleviate stress and clear your mind. To begin your meditation invoke the skill with 'Open Pregnancy Meditations' and follow the prompts. If you like this skill and find it to be a useful addition to your mindfulness practice we would really appreciate if you drop us a review! Any suggestions, questions, or bug reports are welcome at support@stokedskills.com. We'd love to hear your feedback so we can continue to improve our products. Enjoy!
